query:
SELECT
            id,
            server_id,
            registration_id,
            common_access_card_certificate,
            (
                SELECT election_id
                FROM registrations
                WHERE registrations.id = registration_id
                  AND jurisdiction_id = $1
            ),
            (
                SELECT precinct_id
                FROM registrations
                WHERE registrations.id = registration_id
                  AND jurisdiction_id = $1
            ),
            (
                SELECT ballot_style_id
                FROM registrations
                WHERE registrations.id = registration_id
                  AND jurisdiction_id = $1
            ),
            cast_vote_record,
            cast_vote_record_signature,
            created_at
        FROM printed_ballots
        ORDER BY created_at DESC
